{"tid":1022524,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過著拖鞋搭飛機","createTime":"2019-02-15T05:43:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T05:53:26.000Z","uid":172184,"like":748,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":110,"replies":[{"pid":"1357712d8358efc0094466fa35b8d93b0b6a28cb","tid":1022524,"uid":172184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T05:43:58.000Z","msg":"喺台灣讀書<br />\n有年暑假返香港<br />\n喺台灣嗰邊去機場程路上<br />\n落左場勁大雨<br />\n對鞋連襪濕撚曬<br />\n個時喺度諗緊返到香港實臭到仆街<br />\n當時喺高鐵站(唔係台北嗰邊讀)<br />\n9衝左入廁所開喼攞對拖鞋出黎<br />\n順手換埋套濕曬嘅衫 (台灣啲廁所多數都好乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n衰鬼又幾撚正喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc9721c8240198fe75023fefb2d26b73f7746020","tid":1022524,"uid":217334,"like":670,"dislike":12,"score":658,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T05:46:39.000Z","msg":"唔想知"},{"pid":"38c4195e12a50abbd977069cd7a39922c5a7cb82","tid":1022524,"uid":172184,"like":8,"dislike":32,"score":-24,"quote":{"pid":"cc9721c8240198fe75023fefb2d26b73f7746020","tid":1022524,"uid":217334,"like":670,"dislike":12,"score":658,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T05:46:39.000Z","msg":"唔想知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T05:48:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b44bf9eed3d312d11a06d11e12a9e69168fe155","tid":1022524,"uid":67737,"like":487,"dislike":6,"score":481,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T06:04:41.000Z","msg":"之前去泰國，全程都著拖鞋，冇帶其他鞋"},{"pid":"a3729924c6a2c7f8c2fd817d6fc04928f22f002f","tid":1022524,"uid":234317,"like":10,"dislike":372,"score":-